      "body" : "The issue here is that in `decodescript` we do try to parse a `wsh`Â descriptor from a constructed P2WSH scriptPubKey:\r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/2b211b41e36f914b8d0487e698b619039cc3c8e2/src/rpc/rawtransaction.cpp#L519-L530\r\n\r\nBut `inferScript` won't be able to analyze the witness script itself since we are passing a dummy signature provider: \r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/2b211b41e36f914b8d0487e698b619039cc3c8e2/src/core_write.cpp#L150-L156\r\n\r\nTherefore `GetCScript`Â won't return anything:\r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/2b211b41e36f914b8d0487e698b619039cc3c8e2/src/script/descriptor.cpp#L1622-L1629",
